title: The Beatles: Live at the Hollywood Bowl [Bonus Tracks] (2016)
description:
The Beatles first live album, Recorded from live shows in the summers of 1964 and 1965.

2 - She's a Woman
3 - Dizzy Miss Lizzy
4 - Ticket to Ride

10 - Help!
11 - All My Loving
12 - She Loves You
13 - Long Tall Sally
14 - You Can't do That
15 - I Want to Hold your Hand
16 - Everybody's Trying to be my Baby
17 - Baby's in Black
